#=============================
# Cada dispositivo (username = CN del client cert) publica su telemetría y estado,
# y solo lee sus comandos.
pattern write smca/lab/%u/telemetry/#
pattern write smca/lab/%u/status#
pattern read  smca/lab/%u/cmd/#

# El backend con acceso global
user backend_smca
topic read  smca/lab/+/telemetry/#
topic write smca/lab/+/cmd/#
topic read  smca/lab/+/status#